<p>

An update to Counter-Strike Condition Zero and a few game engine changes have just been released on Steam. When you launch any game, you'll receive this update automatically. Condition Zero dedicated servers will need to restart to receive the update.<br/><br/><ul style="padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><b>COUNTER-STRIKE: CONDITION ZERO</b><br/><li>Fixed "bartime" (used by bomb defusal progress bar) being sent by the server in the wrong format</li><br/><br/><b>GAME ENGINE</b> (all Steam games)<br/><li>Added a command line option ("-noaafonts") to disable anti-aliasing on fonts</li><br/><li>Replace "#" with " " if it is the first character in a player's in-game name</li><br/><li>Resolved a graphics-related error in Day of Defeat &amp; Condition Zero Deleted Scenes</li><br/></ul><br/></p>
